The paper deals with caching and delivery in a communication network, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The problem of cache placement and delivery delay optimization is a classic problem in distributed systems (cs.DS) and control theory (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the use of universal schemes, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG).
